item.title: How do I make a silabsoft server?
item.dc:creator: @guitars595 guitars595
item.description:
@guitars595 wrote:

There is no such thing as a Silabsoft server. You can make a server from scratch that is compatible with the Silab client but there is no such thing as a silab server.
